

\section{Getting rid of local variables}

In many cases using local variables within functions maybe unnecessary. One can easily use self-executing functions to replace such variables.

\begin{codeblock}
// with local vars
function withvars(y){
     var x = 12;
     return x + y;
}

log(withvars(12));

// can be written as 
function novars(y){
     //var x = 12;
     return (function(){return 12 + y;})();
}

log(novars(12));
\end{codeblock}















